to the forest I saw Grandpa in?

597
00:55:27,208 --> 00:55:28,333
The forest?

598
00:55:30,458 --> 00:55:31,958
Grandpa!

599
00:55:32,041 --> 00:55:33,125
Grandma!

600
00:55:34,333 --> 00:55:36,750
Mom! Dad!

601
00:55:36,833 --> 00:55:38,875
